snippet.title: PLANET DUNE | A Rescue Mission Turns Into a Fight for Survival | Full Movie
snippet.description:
A rescue team lands on a remote desert planet.
Survival becomes impossible once the planet strikes back.

A crew is sent to investigate and recover a stranded outpost on a distant desert world. What begins as a routine rescue quickly turns dangerous when they discover the planet is home to massive creatures lurking beneath the sands. With communication failing and escape uncertain, the team must work together to survive a hostile environment that offers no mercy.

Director: Glenn Campbell, Tammy Klein
Cast: Sean Young, Emily Killian, Clark Moore.
